quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Random Numbers[/h1]

A [b]for [/b]loop can be used to generate multiple random numbers.[code format="cpp" codeId="240"]int main() {
[b]  for[/b] (int x = 1; x <= 10; x++) {
    cout << [b]rand()[/b] << endl;
  }
}

/* Output: 
41
18467
6334
26500
19169
15724
11478
29358
26962
24464
*/[/code]

